menuconfig MODULES_DDS_PARAM_BRIDGE
	bool "DDS Parameter Bridge"
	default n
	---help---
		Bridge DDS parameter_set_value_request to PX4 param_set() directly.
		Allows ROS2/DDS to modify PX4 parameters without CONFIG_PARAM_PRIMARY
		or CONFIG_ORB_COMMUNICATOR. Required for fmu-v5 and other boards
		that do not support the primary/remote parameter sync mechanism.
